body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting CarPal Customer Support. My name is Jason Hall and I will be assisting you today.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Michelle Cook.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Michelle. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm having a problem with the pricing at one of your Car Dealerships.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I see, I'd like to help. Can you provide me with your phone number so I can look up your account?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's five five five. three two one. four zero nine eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. One more piece of information, could you provide me with the location of the dealership you visited?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, I visited the dealership on two one zero zero Main Street.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing that information, Michelle. I will look into this matter for you. Is there anything else you would like to add before I proceed?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Michelle. I will investigate the pricing matter at the dealership on Main Street and follow up with you soon. Have a great day!
